              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The count rate was corrected for gamma-ray intensity,",
                "detector efficiency, geometry, coincidence losses and",
                "self absorption. In some cases special dead-time cor-",
                "rection was needed."
